import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import vuetify from './plugins/vuetify'
import router from '/src/router'


Vue.config.productionTip = false
require('vuetify-loader')
require('vue-router')

new Vue({
  vuetify,
  router,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
